data.title: Pet Food, Pet Supplies & Pet Products
data.meta_description: Explore a diverse range of high-quality pet food and supplies at Pet Supermarket. Whether you're looking for premium dog and cat food, bird, reptile, or fish supplies, or essential pet toys and grooming products, we have everything your furry, scaly, or finned friend needs. Explore fantastic deals on top-notch pet products and choose to shop conveniently online or in-store today for a happier, healthier pet.
data.text: Offer valid in-store and online for VIP Rewards loyalty members only between 8/26 - 9/28/24. Earn 3X the points on select dog products towards a $5 Reward including all dog leashes and collars, dog flea and tick products, dog clothing and clothing accessories, and dog health & wellness care (health & wellness care includes allergy & immune system care, dewormers, digestive care, eye & ear care, first aid, hip & joint care, skin & coat care, stress & anxiety care, supplements, urinary care and vitamins & minerals), while supplies last. For more details on our VIP Rewards program, please see https://www.petsupermarket.com/vip-terms-and-conditions.html. ​
